section_summary: The text is a part of the opening statement of the National Assembly of Kuwait. It includes greetings and well wishes to the newly elected members of the assembly and the new government. The speaker also emphasizes the importance of fulfilling their responsibilities and living up to the expectations of the Kuwaiti people. The text also mentions the democratic foundations of the country and the need to work towards achieving the trust of the people. The text is dated June 20, 2023, and is on page number 21.
